ace: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">3.<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;">获得五种打造精彩故事的实用工具</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">适合人群：</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">写作爱好者，编剧工作者、学习编剧者、对编剧感兴趣的读者</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">当你有一部好故事，好电影</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">&nbsp; &nbsp;一定会有人愿意带着甘醇的美酒</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">与你不醉不归</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">只需</span>