<p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appQKNOkuRC6696/image/ueditor/30941200_1523322515.gif" title=".gif" alt="0 (9).gif"/><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">你还在为如何写编剧写故事而烦恼吗？</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.75em; text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px;">今天我要告诉你</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">可以和无从下笔笔说再见了</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 