 white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">2011<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;">年转修影视，开始钻研微电影、</span>MTV<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;">拍摄、剧本编排，宣传片制作，获得了许多成就。当时他的作品在优酷土豆广泛传播，作品《二手势大全》、《还不懂愛》，获得千万的点击量，</span>MTV<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;">《最后之前》也受到了业内人士的肯定。</span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appQKNOkuRC6696/image/ueditor/54654700_1523322515.gif" title=".gif" alt="0 (6).gif"/></span></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px;">MV《最后之前》</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">而如今他已经是北京哪吒闹海文化传播有限公司</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px;">CEO</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">，前影创立学院院长，尼康索尼特聘讲师，经常被各大品牌机构邀请线下授课，他的学生已经遍布全国</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px;">30</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">多个省份，都是摄影、影视相关从业人员。<br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">由于潘庆华的亲身经历，他太知道对于编剧工作者、从事写作方面工作或者想写故事的人，没有一套专业的写作思路、思维，以及帮助我们获得灵感的工具，是多磨让人痛苦的事情，摸着石头过河，竟扎脚。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appQKNOkuRC6696/image/ueditor/73813500_1523322515.gif" title=".gif" alt="0 (7).gif"/></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"></span><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">所以，他将自己从事了影视工作近</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px;">7</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">年的经验，以及通过对经典摄影书籍《编剧备忘录》的认真解读，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">打造出了一套人人都可以“复制”的好莱坞剧本模式为自己所用的课程</strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px; font-family: 宋体;">，结合电影赏析、理论讲解以及案例分析，将书中精华知识可视化，把最干的内容奉献给你。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(255, 41, 65);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px;">他一直想对你说：人人都能写出好故事</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">书籍介绍</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appQKNOkuRC6696/image/ueditor/86034800_1523322515.jpg" title=".jpg" alt="0 (5).jpg"/></span></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-size: 15px;"></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><br/></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">《编剧备忘录:故事结构和角色的秘密》通过案例精读和电影剧照、插图、图表的使用，为那些正从事编剧工作、学习编剧或者对编剧感兴趣的读者展示编剧写作流程的概况。书中主要讲解了故事结构的写作，以及角色的安排与性格体现，包括两极对立、实用指南、英雄的内心之旅、交互作用、认识原型及其他角色、故事线、神奇故事公式、环境因素等；将编剧理论和实践相结合，是编剧工作者和初学者一本很好的实用指南和创作灵感的来源。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">课程概述：</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><br/></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">很多经典的电影、电视剧、小说的剧情都非常值得我们反复观看和推敲，它们的剧本心思缜密，节奏有序，主人的人物设定活灵活现，故事情节波澜曲折，而且富有意义。例如《盗梦空间》，它的票房是网友们经过反复观看推上去的；例如《复仇者联盟》，兼具速度与刺激，场面宏大，明星阵容更是强大到没天理，而观众愿意为这样的阵容买单等等。这些电影往往从某种层面上满足了我们本身的诉求、表达和欲望，才使得这些电影获得巨大成功，而这巨大成功的背后，编剧编排写作，成了灵魂所在。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">&nbsp;</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">本书对于写作工作者来说，是非常有帮助，目前最好的赚钱方式就是写作，制作成本也相对较低，只要我们按照一定的方式和方法来进行写作，你也可以写出像《复仇者联盟》、《指环王》一样的故事。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);"><br/></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">摄影读书会潘庆华将再次和大家以视频的方式和大家分享，在本次课程中，潘庆华老师将教给你一些剧本创作的基本常识与实用工具，结合一些具体影片赏析以及我们自己之前看电影的经历，来学习如何设置你的故事结构，打造让观众欲罢不能的好故事。</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136);">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">课程大纲：</strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 18px;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;"><br/></strong></span></p><p style="margin: 0px 16px; font-size: medium; white-space: normal; padding: 0px; clear: both; font-family: &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Helvetica, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; text-align: justify; line-height: 1.75em;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/appQKNOkuRC6696/image/ueditor/92036400_1523322515.j